      "zh": "芳纶纤维是一类耐热且坚固的合成纤维。它们应用于航空航天和军事，用于弹道级的防弹织物和防弹复合材料，自行车轮胎，船舶缆绳，船体增强材料以及石棉替代品。",
      "en": "Aramid fibers are a class of heat-resistant and strong synthetic fabric. They are used in aerospace and military applications, for ballistic-rated body armor fabric and ballistic composites, in bicycle tires, marine cordage, marine hull reinforcement, and as an asbestos substitute."
